# LLM API Gateway — 核心时序图

## 1. LLM 代理请求流程（同步模式）

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor Client as 终端用户
    participant Nginx as Nginx :443
    participant Auth as AuthMiddleware
    participant Quota as QuotaMiddleware
    participant Proxy as ProxyHandler
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant Zhipu as 智谱 API

    Client->>Nginx: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer sk-xxx
    Nginx->>Auth: 转发请求

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Auth,DB: 阶段1: 鉴权
        Auth->>DB: SELECT * FROM users<br/>WHERE sub_key_hash = SHA256(sk-xxx)
        DB-->>Auth: user {id, status}
        alt 子 Key 无效
            Auth-->>Client: 401 Invalid API key
        else 子 Key 已禁用
            Auth-->>Client: 403 Key disabled
        end
    end

    Auth->>Quota: 通过，传递 user_id

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over Quota,DB: 阶段2: 配额检查
        Quota->>DB: SELECT * FROM quotas WHERE user_id = ?
        DB-->>Quota: {quota_5h_used, quota_5h_limit,<br/>quota_total_used, quota_total_limit}
        alt 5h 配额耗尽
            Quota-->>Client: 429 "5h quota exceeded"
        else 总配额耗尽
            Quota-->>Client: 429 "Total quota exceeded"
        end
    end

    Quota->>Proxy: 准入，传递 user_id + 请求

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Proxy,Zhipu: 阶段3: 代理转发
        Proxy->>Proxy: 构建上游请求<br/>注入真实 API Key
        Proxy->>Zhipu: POST https://api.zhipuai.cn/v1/chat/completions
        Zhipu-->>Proxy: 200 {choices, usage: {total_tokens: 60}}
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        Note over Proxy,DB: 阶段4: 配额确认 + 日志
        Proxy->>DB: UPDATE quotas<br/>SET quota_5h_used += 60,<br/>quota_total_used += 60<br/>WHERE user_id = ?
        Proxy->>DB: INSERT INTO call_logs<br/>(user_id, total_tokens, status_code, latency_ms)
    end

    Proxy->>Client: 200 {choices, usage: {total_tokens: 60}}
```

---

## 2. Admin 创建用户流程

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin as 管理员
    participant Nginx as Nginx
    participant AdminAPI as AdminHandler
    participant Auth as AuthMiddleware
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant KeyGen as KeyGenerator

    Admin->>Nginx: POST /admin/api/users<br/>Cookie: admin_session=xxx
    Nginx->>Auth: 会话鉴权

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Auth,DB: 验证 Admin Session
        Auth->>DB: SELECT * FROM admin_sessions<br/>WHERE session_token = ? AND expires_at > now
        alt Session 无效
            Auth-->>Admin: 401 未登录
        end
    end

    Auth->>AdminAPI: 通过

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over AdminAPI,KeyGen: 创建用户
        AdminAPI->>KeyGen: GenerateSubKey(userID)
        KeyGen-->>AdminAPI: sk-3f8a2b1c...
        AdminAPI->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
        AdminAPI->>DB: INSERT INTO users<br/>(username, sub_key_hash, sub_key_preview, role)
        AdminAPI->>DB: INSERT INTO quotas<br/>(user_id, quota_5h_limit, quota_total_limit)
        AdminAPI->>DB: COMMIT
    end

    AdminAPI-->>Admin: 201 {user, sub_key: "sk-3f8a2b1c...", quotas}
    Note over Admin,KeyGen: ⚠️ 子 Key 明文仅此一次返回<br/>后续无法获取
```

---

## 3. 用户自助查询配额流程

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor Client as 终端用户
    participant Auth as AuthMiddleware
    participant QuotaH as QuotaHandler
    participant DB as SQLite

    Client->>Auth: GET /v1/quota<br/>Authorization: Bearer sk-xxx

    Auth->>DB: 子 Key 鉴权
    DB-->>Auth: user_id = 2

    Auth->>QuotaH: 通过

    QuotaH->>DB: SELECT q.*, u.status<br/>FROM quotas q JOIN users u<br/>ON q.user_id = u.id<br/>WHERE q.user_id = 2
    DB-->>QuotaH: {quota_5h_limit, quota_5h_used,<br/>quota_total_limit, quota_total_used,<br/>window_start, status}

    QuotaH-->>Client: 200 {<br/>  quota_5h_remaining: 550000,<br/>  quota_total_remaining: 97700000,<br/>  window_reset_at: "15:00",<br/>  status: "active"<br/>}
```
